Clinical training will range will range from indirect (veneers, single crowns, onlays, crown and bridge) to direct restorations, as well as the latest in bleaching techniques. To register for this program, please call Jarett J. Gilbert, Director, at (212) 998-9757.                                                       Click flyer above to learn more and complete the Registration Form, which has fillable fields. Form must be downloaded, then opened with Adobe Acrobat. After filling in fields electronically on the downloaded file, select "File > Send" and email the completed form to dentalcde@nyu.edu. Visit www.adobe.com to learn more about Adobe products. Clinical training will range will range from indirect (veneers, single crowns, onlays, crown and bridge) to direct restorations, as well as the latest in bleaching techniques.
